  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n*Summary*: when you have long chat history with TTT paid, you always will see  \"Tribute paid\" message when open this chat. This message jumps to the start of history when scrolling.  Part of https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/8304 (was found in https://github.com/status-im/status-react/pull/8304#issuecomment-498204108)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\ncan see last 10 messages, \"Tribute paid\" message is not shown until I will scroll manually to the start of the history\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\"Tribute paid\" message is shown\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- create 2 accounts (A and B)\r\n- change network to Ropsten\r\n- as user A: set TTT\r\n- as user B: pay TTT and send message to user A\r\n- as user B: send 10+ messages to user A\r\n- go back and open chat with user A again\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n- Status version: develop 03/01/2019 with enabled TTT \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n- Video:  https://drive.google.com/open?id=1KxhDHWkruqATKLr3Q9rPR_9qSTeBRlSq\r\n",
